Released December 21, 2021. Happy Holidays!
New Features:
Step:
- Mode: Normal; Bypasses NCP configs
- Mode: Vanilla; Vanilla Step, does not work on strict servers
- Height; Maximum step height
Speed:
- Mode: Strafe; Automatically jumps and gains speed, Bypasses NCP configs
- Mode: StrafeStrict; Automatically jumps and gains speed, Bypasses Updated NCP configs
- Boost; Boosts speed when taking knockback
- StrictCollision; Strict collision speed reset
- StrictSprint; Keeps sprint while moving
- QuickStart; Allows speed to be quickly gained after a collision
AntiVoid:
- Mode: Suspend; Stops all vertical motion
NewChunks
- Height; The height to render the new chunk at
AntiAFK
- Chat; Send messages in the chat to avoid AFK detection, automatically responds to direct messages
- Jump; Jumps to avoid AFK detection
Nametags:
- Background; Displays a background behind the nametags
- Healthbar; Visualizes the player's health
- DistanceScale; Scales the nametags size by the distance from the entity
- SimpleEnchantments; Simplifies the enchantment display
Colors
- Rainbow; Changes the client color scheme to a cycling RGB value
